Ex-BBN reality star Angel has stated she is ‘proud’ to have relocated from Nigeria. Referring to Nigeria as “that country”, she said everything about her becomes better whenever she travels out. The controversial reality star said she is glad to have “escaped” the harsh realities of Nigeria.   Grateful Blessing CEO celebrates at 33     I keep getting credit alerts from strangers – Nkechi…     Singer Olamide makes U-turn, gifts berated fan car   She wrote: “Proud to say that i have relocated out of Naija.” In another tweet, she said: ”I’m happiest when I’m out of that country. My skin glows more, i put on happy weight and my brain is more relaxed.”